his sub-agent session is just processing a scheduled job, I should report no active conversations.","thinkingSignature":"6d5a468d92351f0f35d31fecc128cf25351b2504cbc515409c2bf1eb5f6c7b3c"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习。\n\n当前有1个活跃子Agent会话（feishu渠道，更新于约3分钟前），说明存在进行中的后台任务，不属于空闲状态。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2025,"output":448,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46454,"cost":{"input":0.0006075,"output":0.0005376,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00246453}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774675435989}}
